---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pricing"
  description="Flexible pricing plans for AI agent automation. Start with a discovery sprint, scale with enterprise features."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-hero-pattern">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-blue/10 to-signal-green/10"></div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
          Simple, transparent <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-blue to-signal-green bg-clip-text text-transparent">pricing</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300 sm:text-xl">
          Start your automation journey with a discovery sprint. Scale with flexible plans as you grow.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Plans -->
  <section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
        <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
          Choose your automation path
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="isolate mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-md grid-cols-1 gap-y-8 sm:mt-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-4">
        <!-- Discovery Sprint -->
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white/5 p-8 ring-1 ring-white/10 xl:p-10">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-x-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8">Discovery Sprint</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
              Perfect for understanding your automation opportunities.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-6 flex items-baseline gap-x-1">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">$15K</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-300">2-week engagement</span>
            </p>
            <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-accent-blue" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Process assessment & automation roadmap
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-accent-blue" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                POC implementation
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-accent-blue" viewView="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                ROI projections & business case
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-accent-blue" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Technical architecture plan
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 block rounded-md bg-accent-blue px-3 py-2 text-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-blue-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-accent-blue">
            Book Discovery
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Pilot -->
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white/5 p-8 ring-1 ring-white/10 xl:p-10">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-x-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8">Pilot</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
              Production-ready implementation for your first use case.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-6 flex items-baseline gap-x-1">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">$50K</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-300">6-week implementation</span>
            </p>
            <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-signal-green" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Single workflow automation
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-signal-green" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Basic governance & monitoring
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-signal-green" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Team training & documentation
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-signal-green" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                30 days support included
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 block rounded-md bg-signal-green px-3 py-2 text-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-green-600 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-signal-green">
            Start Pilot
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Platform Subscription -->
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-b from-accent-blue/10 to-signal-green/10 p-8 ring-2 ring-accent-blue xl:p-10">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-x-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-accent-blue">Platform</h3>
              <p class="rounded-full bg-accent-blue/10 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-semibold leading-5 text-accent-blue">
                Most popular
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
              Full platform access with enterprise features and support.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-6 flex items-baseline gap-x-1">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">$10K</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-300">/month</span>
            </p>
            <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-accent-blue" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Unlimited workflows & agents
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-accent-blue" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Advanced governance & compliance
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-accent-blue" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                SSO & enterprise integrations
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-accent-blue" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                24/7 support & CSM
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 block rounded-md bg-accent-blue px-3 py-2 text-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-blue-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-white">
            Contact Sales
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Managed Operations -->
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white/5 p-8 ring-1 ring-white/10 xl:p-10">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-x-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8">Managed Ops</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
              We manage your automation infrastructure end-to-end.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-6 flex items-baseline gap-x-1">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Custom</span>
            </p>
            <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-purple-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Dedicated engineering team
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-purple-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Custom workflow development
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-purple-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                SLA guarantees & monitoring
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-x-3">
                <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none text-purple-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Continuous optimization
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 block rounded-md bg-purple-600 px-3 py-2 text-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-purple-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-purple-600">
            Discuss Requirements
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="bg-gray-900 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl divide-y divide-white/10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold leading-10 tracking-tight">Frequently asked questions</h2>
        <dl class="mt-10 space-y-6 divide-y divide-white/10">
          <div class="pt-6">
            <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">
              Can I deploy on-premises or in my private cloud?
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
              Yes, all plans support deployment in your preferred environment. We support AWS, Azure, GCP, and on-premises Kubernetes clusters.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-6">
            <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">
              What's included in the Discovery Sprint?
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
              Process analysis, automation opportunity assessment, POC implementation, ROI projections, and technical architecture recommendations. You'll have a clear roadmap within 2 weeks.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-6">
            <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">
              How do you ensure compliance and security?
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
              Built-in compliance frameworks (SOC2, GDPR, HIPAA), comprehensive audit logging, fine-grained access controls, and data residency options. All workflows run with your governance policies enforced.
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-6">
            <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">
              What integrations are available?
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
              Native integrations with Jira, ServiceNow, Slack, GitHub, Kubernetes, major databases, and email systems. Custom integrations available via REST APIs and webhooks.
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-primary-bg">
    <div class="px-6 py-24 sm:px-6 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
          Ready to start your automation journey?
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
          Book a discovery sprint to understand your opportunities and build a business case.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6 flex-wrap">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="rounded-md bg-accent-blue px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors"
          >
            Book Discovery Sprint
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white hover:text-accent-blue transition-colors"
          >
            Talk to Sales <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>